---
export const prerender = true;

import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Arnab Dey" description="Photographs paired with verse — the story behind the work of Arnab Dey.">
  <section class="page-head">
    <div class="container-narrow text-center">
      <span class="eyebrow">About</span>
      <h1>Light &amp; Language</h1>
      <hr class="divider" />
      <p>One pair of eyes, two ways of paying attention.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="content-wrapper" style="padding-top: 0;">
    <div class="prose">
      <p>I make two things that turn out to be the same thing: photographs and poems. A picture is a held breath; a poem is the caption the breath was waiting for. This site is where I let them keep each other company.</p>

      <p>Most of what you'll find here is built around a single idea — the <em>plate</em>: one image, a few lines of verse, nothing else competing for your attention. Some poems stand on their own. Some photographs prefer the silence. But the work I care about most lives in the pairing.</p>

      <h2>The work</h2>
      <p>I'm drawn to quiet — early light on water, a single figure in a loud city, the ordinary made briefly strange. I shoot to slow down, and I write to remember why I stopped.</p>

      <blockquote>Every photograph is a story waiting to be told, and every poem is a world waiting to be seen.</blockquote>

      <h2>Prints</h2>
      <p>Many of the photographs are available as fine-art prints, made to order on archival paper. If an image asks to live on your wall, you can bring it home from the <a href="/store">print store</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-links">
      <a href="/photography">The Gallery &rarr;</a>
      <a href="/poetry">The Verse &rarr;</a>
      <a href="/store">The Prints &rarr;</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-head { padding: clamp(8rem, 16vh, 12rem) 0 clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem); }
  .about-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 2rem;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 3.5rem;
    padding-top: 2.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .about-links a {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .about-links a:hover { color: var(--gold); }
</style>
